data.description:
Welcome to the country! Located at the end of a private road this newly remodeled home is bright and open throughout. Large teak decks on the front and back, one acre of fenced pasture with large hay and storage sheds. Inside are large windows throughout the open main living space. Updated kitchen with large pantry. Bathrooms boast Italian stone tile. Primary bedroom has a private entry and deck. It's ensuit bathroom has a large shower and soaking tub. 
Only 8 miles from Driggs and less than an hour from Jackson Hole!
